shopifyProducts.title: Aere Cool Gel Crystal Waterproof Mattress Protectors 10"-18" By Legget & Platt
shopifyProducts.description:
Aere Cool Gel Crystal Waterproof Mattress Protector

The Aere Crystal Gel Mattress Protector offers a breathable, 100% waterproof barrier designed to enhance the performance and longevity of your mattress. This protector not only shields your mattress from sweat, dead skin cells, liquid spills, dust mites, and mold buildup but also ensures a hygienic and comfortable sleeping environment. Over time, these factors can cause staining and potentially void your mattress warranty.

Features & Specifications:

  • Innovative Cooling Crystal Gel Fibers: Absorbs and dissipates heat away from the body for an ultra-cool sleep experience.
  • Revolutionary Tactile Technology 3D Fabric: Machine washable, promotes excellent airflow, and aids in moisture evaporation.
  • Dust Mite and Pet Dander Barrier: Provides a protective shield against common allergens.
  • Luxurious Stretch Fabric: Conforms to the mattress without altering its feel, ensuring a peaceful sleep.
  • Deep Corner Pockets: Stretch to fit the mattress securely and easily.

Available Sizes & Dimensions:

  • California King: 72" x 84" up to 18"

Shipping Details:

  • We provide free White Glove Delivery within Los Angeles County, including setup, removal of old bed, and packaging disposal.

Warranty:
10-year warranty against manufacturing defects.

Return Policy:
Due to its use as a personal item, protectors may not be returned.
